0x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Victorious@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Victorious@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Victorious@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>第一批参加 2025 年胜利音乐节的艺术家已经确定，其中<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kings-of-leon">Kings Of Leon</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queens-of-the-stone-age">Queens Of The Stone Age</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/vampire-weekend">Vampire Weekend</a>处于领先地位。请在下面了解更多详细信息。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/kings-of-leon-can-we-please-have-fun-3753952">莱昂之王如何恢复自信：“我们还没有准备好放弃”</a></strong></li></ul><p>明年的现场音乐活动（英国最大的都市音乐节）将于 8 月 22 日至 24 日期间重返南海海滨。</p><p>随着新的宣布，石器时代女王已被确认为头条新闻，并将在为期三天的活动的第一天（8 月 22 日星期五）登上舞台。今年夏天，他们为庆祝最新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/queens-of-the-stone-age-in-times-new-room-review-3455962">《In Times New Roman》</a>而进行了重要的巡演，而主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/josh-homme">乔什·霍姆 (Josh Homme)</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/queens-of-the-stone-age-cancel-european-shows-due-to-josh-homme-needing-emergency-surgery-3773173">在接受紧急手术后</a>重返舞台后，该节目也随之推出。</p><p>由于节日的进展顺利，因此是吸血鬼周末被定为周六分期付款的头条新闻（8月23日）。对于<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ezra-koenig">以斯拉·科尼格（Ezra Koenig</a> and Co），该节目在发行了新唱片<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/vampire-weekend-only-god-was-above-us-review-3613120">《只有上帝在我们之上》</a>之后，并在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/vampire-weekend-add-extra-brixton-academy-show-to-2024-uk-and-ireland-tour-buy-tickets-3749797">英国和爱尔兰</a>进行了巨大的旅行之后。</p><p>最终，莱昂国王队的第三个也是最后一个头条新闻排在2025年胜利的最后一天。他们在周日（8月24日）将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kings-of-leon-announce-huge-summer-2025-uk-shows-in-cardiff-and-lytham-3817790">在Cardiff和Lytham举行的两个巨大的夏季演出</a>之后，他们在周日的节日结束，并看到他们从第九张录音室专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kings-of-leon-can-we-please-have-fun-review-3750216">《我们可以玩得开心》</a>中脱颖而出。 </p><figure id="attachment_3762820" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3762820" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3762820" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Kings-of-Leon@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Leon Kings的Caleb Clastill于2024年在舞台上演出" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Kings-of-Leon@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Kings-of-Leon@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Kings-of-Leon@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Kings-of-Leon@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Kings-of-Leon@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Kings-of-Leon@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3762820" class="wp-caption-text"> Leon Kings的Caleb Clastill在2024年在舞台上表演。</figcaption></figure><p>胜利的最后一晚加入莱昂国王将是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bloc-party">Bloc Party</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gabrielle">Gabrielle</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/reytons">Reytons</a> ，而周六的阵容还将包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nelly-furtado">Nelly Furtado</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">最后的晚宴</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/travis">Travis</a> 。</p><p>在2025年活动的开幕之夜之前，将是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-kiwanuka">迈克尔·基瓦努卡（Michael Kiwanuka）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/madness">疯狂（Madness）</a> ，而来自三个晚上的DJ套装将来自<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/melanie-c">梅兰妮（Melanie）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mike-skinner">迈克·斯金纳（Mike Skinner）</a> ，下午特别的客座老虎机由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-charlatans">charlatans</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rizzle-kicks">rizzle kicks</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/craig-david">Craig</a>填补<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/craig-david">大卫</a>。</p><p>其他艺术家在此公告中证实，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shed-seven">七人，丹尼尔</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/daniel-bedingfield">·贝丁菲尔德（Daniel Bedingfield）</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/reverend-and-the-makers">牧师和制造商</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-zutons">Zutons</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/caity-baser">Caity Baser</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jamie-webster">Jamie Webster</a> ，Jamie Webster， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/everything-everything">Everything</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-mary-wallopers">The Mary Wallopers</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wunderhorse">Wunderhorse</a> ，Wunderhorse， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-ks">K&#39;s，K&#39;s</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/scouting-for-girls">Girls for Girls for Girls for Girls for Girls</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bradley-simpson">Bradley Simpson</a> ，The Waeve， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-waeve">The Waeve</a> ，更多。</p><p> “我们已经为2025年的胜利的2025年预订了标志性的头条新闻和新兴的人才。我们始终希望为粉丝提供最佳价值，并努力创造一个真正为每个人提供的周末。</p><p> “胜利的2025年有望令人难忘的表演，回忆和千载难逢的经历！我们迫不及待地想再次看到Southsea Seafront上的每个人！” </p><figure id="attachment_3762996" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3762996" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3762996" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/josh-homme-roberto-riccuti-getty-1.jpg" alt="乔什·霍姆（Josh Homme）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/josh-homme-roberto-riccuti-getty-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/josh-homme-roberto-riccuti-getty-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/josh-homme-roberto-riccuti-getty-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/josh-homme-roberto-riccuti-getty-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/josh-homme-roberto-riccuti-getty-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/josh-homme-roberto-riccuti-getty-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3762996" class="wp-caption-text">乔什·霍姆（Josh Homme）。图片来源：Roberto Ricciuti/Getty</figcaption></figure><p>除了为活动预定的大量艺术家外，乔尔·多梅特（Joel Dommett）和鲁比·瓦克斯（Ruby Wax）还被宣布为2025年的胜利喜剧阵容。</p><p>明年胜利的门票现已开始销售，早鸟门票每天70英镑，周末的票价为180英镑。<a href="https://www.victoriousfestival.co.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处</a>获取门票和更多信息。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/victorious-festival-announces-headliners-for-2024-buy-tickets-3553549">今年的胜利节</a>在八月的银行假期周末（8月23日至25日）席卷，并看到<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fatboy-slim">Fatboy Slim</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/snow-patrol">Snow Patrol共同领导了</a>节日的星期五晚上，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jamie-t">Jamie T</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/biffy-clyro">Biffy Clyro</a>在周六和周日，周日和周日的账单上登上了账单分别。</p><p>阵容中也是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wet-leg">湿腿</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/becky-hill">贝基山</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pixies">小精灵</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/courteeners">骑车者</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/idles">闲置</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jess-glynne">杰西·格林恩</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arlo-parks">阿洛公园</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/soft-play">软玩具</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-lightning-seeds">闪电种子</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/maximo-park">马克西莫公园</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-snuts">snuts</a> ，snuts，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yard-act">院子表演</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-lottery-winners">彩票赢家</a>等。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kings-of-leon-queens-of-the-stone-age-vampire-weekend-to-headline-victorious-festival-2025-line-up-buy-tickets-3818197">莱昂的邮政国王，石器时代的皇后区，吸血鬼周末，标题为2025年的胜利节阵容，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
